Changes in 0.2.4
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Released: 2022-03-16

* Drop custom `local` default for timezone, now uses system configured
  default.

Changes in 0.2.3
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Released: 2022-02-08

* Fix handling of escape and quote in Exec and PodmanArgs keys.

Changes in 0.2.2
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Released: 2021-12-21

* Support enabling services at boot, using the Install section.

Changes in 0.2.1
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Released: 2021-10-14

* Added support for systemd --user services.
* Set PODMAN_SYSTEMD_UNIT in the podman env, enabling podman auto-update support.
